" O 0[8] "Product Information. Farydak (panobinostat)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 'Fesoterodine, Calcium chloride, Phenazopyridine, Sildenafil, Trospium, Mirabegron, Alprostadil, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Flavoxate, Avanafil, More', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Bortezomib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, Pegaspargase, Ixazomib, More', 1767369485);
