formation. Apokyn (apomorphine)." Mylan Pharmaceuticals Inc, Morgantown, WV.', 'Pentosan polysulfate, Phenazopyridine, Alprostadil, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Avanafil, Phenyl salicylate, Ammonium chloride, Dimethyl sulfoxide', NULL, 1767369485);
